---
title: Integration & Automation Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Staff as Operations Staff
    participant CRM as CRM (System of Record)
    participant INT as Integration Layer
    participant EC as eCommerce Platform
    participant COMMS as Automation Engine
    actor Learner as Learner / Resource

    Note over Staff,Learner: ── New Course Offering ──
    Staff->>CRM: Create Event Course record
    CRM->>INT: Trigger: New Event Course
    INT->>EC: Create listing + set inventory count

    Note over Staff,Learner: ── Enrollment ──
    Learner->>EC: Purchase course
    EC->>INT: Purchase webhook
    INT->>CRM: Create Course Seat (Status: Enrolled)
    CRM->>COMMS: Trigger: Seat Status = Enrolled
    COMMS->>Learner: Send enrollment confirmation

    Note over Staff,Learner: ── Weekly Roster ──
    CRM->>COMMS: Scheduled trigger (weekly)
    COMMS->>Learner: Send upcoming week roster to assigned resources

    Note over Staff,Learner: ── Program Completion ──
    Staff->>CRM: Update Course Seat Status = Complete
    CRM->>COMMS: Trigger: Status = Complete
    COMMS->>Learner: Send post-program documentation

    Note over Staff,Learner: ── Cancellation ──
    Staff->>CRM: Cancel Event Course
    CRM->>INT: Trigger: Event Course Status = Cancelled
    INT->>EC: Remove / flag listing; release inventory
    CRM->>COMMS: Trigger: Cancellation notification
    COMMS->>Learner: Send cancellation notice
